name: Banana Swing
description:
Swing on vines to avoid the chasing monkey behind you! Click and hold on vines to grab them(You must be precise!) Build up momentum and get a high score!

Created with Adan's Workshop

(All tiles are 8x8 in size, the monkey sprite is made out of 4 different sprites and the banana is 2 seperate sprites. Some tiles are in tilesheets)
